# SOVIRA Styling Conventions

## Primary CTA Button

Use the following class for primary CTAs:

group relative px-8 py-4 bg-sovira-black text-sovira-paper font-neue-haas font-bold text-lg rounded-sm whitespace-nowrap hover:shadow-sovira-cta hover:-translate-y-px active:translate-y-0 transition-all duration-150

Always include an arrow with hover animation.
